quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  71,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  71,1,hum ne Nooh ko un ki qoum ki taraf bheja ke peshtar is ke ke un par dard dainay wala azaab waqay ho apni qoum ko hadaayat kardo
  71,2,unhon ne kaha ke ae qoum! mein tum ko khulay tor par nasiyaat karta hon
  71,3,ke khuda ki abat karo aur is se daro aur mera kaha manu
  71,4,woh tumahray gunah bakhash day ga aur ( mout ke ) waqt muqarara taq tum ko mohlat ataa kere ga. jab khuda ka muqarrarkiya hoga waqt ajata hai to takheer nahi hoti. kash tum jantay hotay
  71,5,jab logon ne nah maana to ( Nooh ne ) khuda se arz ki ke perwar-digaar mein apni qoum ko raat din bulaataa raha
  71,6,lekin mere bulanay se woh aur ziyada Guzir karte rahay
  71,7,jab jab mein ne un ko bulaya ke ( tauba karen aur ) to un ko maaf farmaiye to unhon ne apne kaanon mein ungelian day len aur kapray ourh liye aur urr gay aur akarr baithy
  71,8,phir mein un ko khulay tor par bhi bulaataa raha
  71,9,aur zahir aur posheeda har terhan samajhata raha
  71,10,aur kaha ke apne perwar-digaar se maffi mango ke woh bara maaf karne wala hai
  71,11,woh tum par aasman se lagataar meen barsaye ga
  71,12,aur maal aur beton se tumhari madad farmaiye ga aur tumhe baagh ataa kere ga aur un mein tumahray liye nehrain baha day ga
  71,13,tum kokiya howa hai ke tum khuda ki Azmat ka aitqaad nahi rakhtay
  71,14,halaank is ne tum ko terhan terhan ( ki halaton ) ka pedakiya hai
  71,15,kiya tum ne nahi dekha ke khuda ne saat aasman kaisay oopar taley banaye hain
  71,16,aur chaand ko un mein ( zameen ka ) noor banaya hai aur Sooraj ko chairag thehraya hai
  71,17,aur khuda hi ne tum ko zameen se pedakiya hai
  71,18,phir isi mein tumhe lota day ga aur ( isi se ) tum ko nikaal khara kere ga
  71,19,aur khuda hi ne zameen ko tumahray liye farsh banaya
  71,20,taakay is ke barray barray kushadah rustoon mein chalo phiro
  71,21,( is ke baad ) Nooh ne arz ki ke mere perwar-digaar! yeh log mere kehnay par nahi chalay aur aison ke tabay hue jin ko un ke maal aur aulaad ne nuqsaan ke siwa kuch faida nahi diya
  71,22,aur woh barri barri chaalein chalay
  71,23,aur kehnay lagey ke apne mabodon ko hargiz nah chhorna aur with aur Sawa aur Yaghus aur Yaqoob aur nasar ko kabhi tark nah karna
  71,24,( perwar-digaar ) unhon ne bohat logon ko gumraah kardiya hai. to too un ko aur gumraah kardey
  71,25,( aakhir ) woh apne gunaaho ke sabab pehlay garqaab kardiye gay phir aag mein daal diye gay. to unhon ne khuda ke siwa kisi ko apna madadgaar nah paaya
  71,26,aur ( phir ) Nooh ne ( yeh ) dua ki ke mere perwar-digaar agar kisi kafir ko roye zameen par basa nah rehne day
  71,27,agar tum un ko rehne day ga to tairay bundon ko gumraah karen ge aur un se jo aulaad hogi woh bhi badkaar aur na shukar guzaar hogi
  71,28,ae mere perwar-digaar mujh ko aur mere maa baap ko aur jo imaan laa kar mere ghar mein aeye is ko aur tamam imaan walay mardon aur imaan wali aurton ko maaf farma aur zalim logon ke liye aur ziyada tabahi barha
